bsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 n\u01a1i trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca</strong></span>. Anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Pique l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc nong Barca mua Clement Lenglet thay Umtiti hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Barca mua Clement Lenglet thay Umtiti h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Cuc-nong-Barca-mua-Clement-Lenglet-thay-Umtiti-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Samuel Umtiti c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Umtiti gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. MU, Chelsea, PSG v\u00e0 Real Madrid l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 MU hay Chelsea \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/samuel-umtiti-44432.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Umtiti</strong></span>, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca nh\u1eafm Clement Lenglet thay Umtiti</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Umtiti gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Theo Sport, Barca mua Clement Lenglet c\u1ee7a Sevilla trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Umtiti ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mua Clement Lenglet\" title=\"Barca mua Clement Lenglet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/barca-nham-hau-ve-sevilla-thay-umtiti.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mua Clement Lenglet thay Umtiti</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Sevilla, v\u00e0 Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hai-doi-bong-thanh-manchester-dai-chien-vi-sao-sevilla-172-174174.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MU c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Lenglet</strong></span>, Mourinho c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo Sport, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Clement Lenglet th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cao h\u01a1n MU, b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLenglet \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla d\u00f9 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t, tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n, ngo\u00e0i ra anh c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Sevilla ngo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Clement Lenglet \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/191986-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Clement Lenglet \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: ju