</h2>\r\n<h2>Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld \u0111ang l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p HLV Pochettino \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt voi gia chuyen nhuong ky luc CLB hinh anh\" title=\"Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c CLB h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Tottenham-mua-Matthijs-de-Ligt-voi-gia-chuyen-nhuong-ky-luc-CLB-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Toby Alderweireld s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nVi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao Atletico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho Alderweireld, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-cho-mu-hoac-chelsea-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-183449.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld </strong></span>n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, nh\u01b0ng MU hay Chelsea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Alderweireld ra \u0111i, Spurs s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Toby Alderweireld ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Metro \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt\" title=\"Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/tottenham-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-vi-sao-18-tuoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ajax, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y anh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan v\u1edbi 29 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1999 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m88 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t, ngo\u00e0i ra anh c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 (\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho De Ligt nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ajax nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/tottenham-hotspur-5.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tottenham</strong></span> ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 18 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham chi 50 trieu bang mua Matthijs de Ligt\" title=\"Tottenham chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Matthijs de Ligt\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Matthijs-de-Ligt-2.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Matthijs de Ligt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nN\u1ebfu Tottenham mua Matthijs de Ligt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/davinson-sanchez-148108.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Davinson Sanchez</strong></span> \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Spurs. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng&rdquo; ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sanchez t\u1eeb Ajax.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Matthijs de Ligt \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/815732-41126/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Matthijs de Ligt \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"791","checkdouble":"183511"},{"date":"13:33 04/04","title":"Liverpool chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Torres","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/4/liverpool-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-torres.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px