align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Ferran Torres cua Valencia voi gia khong tuong hinh anh\" title=\"Liverpool mua Ferran Torres c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Liverpool-mua-Ferran-Torres-cua-Valencia-voi-gia-khong-tuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Ferran Torres \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTorres t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i U17 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Valencia \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i&rdquo; \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 18.&nbsp;Nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ferran Torres khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/jurgen-klopp-20.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Klopp</strong></span> t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. C\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n Liverpool chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Ferran Torres</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool </strong></span>mua Ferran Torres c\u1ee7a Valencia, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool co the chi dam cho Ferran Torres\" title=\"Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Ferran Torres\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/liverpool-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-torres.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Ferran Torres</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi Valencia, anh c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021. Liverpool s\u1ebd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Guillem Balague c\u1ee7a Sky Sports, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Ferran Torres, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u00fac.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, The Kop s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc 20 tri\u1ec7u euro, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Valencia thu v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal</strong></span>, Atletico v\u00e0 Dortmund c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i, song Valencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Mestalla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Ferran Torres kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Valencia v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Mestalla \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"790","checkdouble":"183512"},{"date":"11:39 04/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan vs Inter Milan 23h30 ng\u00e0y 4/4 (Serie A 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/4/nhan-dinh-ac-milan-vs-inter-milan-23h30-ngay-44-serie-a-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;h